{"id": 1788, "genre": 1001, "title": "你有哪些低调的追星行为？", "description": "比如，喜欢一个导演，彻夜看了他所有的影片。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2556, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201707111606230Z2Uanw7mT1MOAHW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-11T03:00:20Z", "options": [{"id": 220672, "content": "出新歌就赶快听，但绝不涉入各家爱豆的争吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825806}, {"id": 221441, "content": "一段时间只循环播放一首歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787171}, {"id": 220674, "content": "从来没有低调过 爱谁就恨不得全世界知道 朋友圈安利的都是他 是的 我爱大张伟", "image": "img/option/option/20170711172758wUgKbOlRqZM93vX4.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945901}, {"id": 220675, "content": "刷完全部综艺舞台，默默去了力所能及的所有现场", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039932}, {"id": 221699, "content": "周杰伦在新歌声当导师，有学员唱杰伦的歌和选杰伦都会很开心?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125594}, {"id": 220676, "content": "喜欢henry rollins \n默默的选择余生都做一个朋克", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066841}, {"id": 220678, "content": "默默关注作品，有时候彻夜追，不发表评论。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076047}, {"id": 221702, "content": "看遍了他导的几十部电影，然后该干什么干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028548}, {"id": 221958, "content": "就因为张云雷唱了好心分手，我苦学这首歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021759}, {"id": 222470, "content": "喜欢上了一个运动员，看了他所有的比赛视频和商演视频，并且学会了辨认6种四周跳的起跳。祝他平昌卫冕成功！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081167}, {"id": 221191, "content": "关注", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076966}, {"id": 221447, "content": "爱豆出单曲出专辑上杂志二话不说找代购买 上电影第一时间找代购买前售券", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871628}, {"id": 220680, "content": "低调地追星", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076053}, {"id": 221704, "content": "没有，不出名的歌手算么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078063}, {"id": 222473, "content": "你低调没事别白嫖啥事不做", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069534}, {"id": 230153, "content": "收藏照片，听歌，看剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107687}, {"id": 222218, "content": "哥哥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079920}, {"id": 220939, "content": "默默关注，看到他的社交更新就开心好久。。。玺。。嘻嘻嘻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010743}, {"id": 220688, "content": "喜欢一个导演 就算他宣传摆渡人 我也会去看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 220689, "content": "喜欢的是死了1800年的人，于是天天上知网看关于他的论文", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015302}, {"id": 220690, "content": "点赞胡歌所有的微博包括广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 220691, "content": "去看个他出演的烂片", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 220692, "content": "学他自杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458710}, {"id": 220693, "content": "所有壁纸都换成了他。关注他的微博，贴吧，但永远潜水。看完他所有综艺，作品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892295}, {"id": 221717, "content": "在他（她）出了口碑较好的作品时去看一下，相当之低调。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903757}, {"id": 222229, "content": "关注下新闻   作品算吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080082}, {"id": 222741, "content": "睡了ta", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081488}, {"id": 220694, "content": "彻夜看了他所有的电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076109}, {"id": 222230, "content": "早起偷偷照镜子……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937472}, {"id": 220695, "content": "关注微博、听演唱会、看爱豆的电影就是不加入官方粉丝会～素不素低调追星哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076113}, {"id": 220696, "content": "把他的专辑封面，电影截图换成头像。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003934}, {"id": 220697, "content": "收藏了网易云算追星吗?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313391}, {"id": 221722, "content": "有时候会看一个人演过的所有影片，看完所有相关的综艺节目，然后买一件T恤就当是做完这些事情的ending", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268915}, {"id": 220699, "content": "老鳖唱的歌，都喜欢，全部无粪曲。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801229}, {"id": 220700, "content": "追星…默默喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074217}, {"id": 220701, "content": "不会说特别喜欢谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999675}, {"id": 220702, "content": "最多会看一下演唱会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999675}, {"id": 220703, "content": "去看东蛋 去看阪蛋 武道馆 代代木", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618722}, {"id": 220704, "content": "乔丹退役后，没看过一场篮球比赛。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703316}, {"id": 221216, "content": "买了他所有的书来看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895868}, {"id": 220705, "content": "为了喜欢的张艺谋，在好奇心评论里骂编辑，还不够，主动投诉到好奇心投诉那", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546490}, {"id": 221217, "content": "别人说自己偶像，也不敢维护", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076990}, {"id": 220706, "content": "默默喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780229}, {"id": 231714, "content": "Yy", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 220707, "content": "角色粉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076134}, {"id": 220708, "content": "密码设成他生日", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051203}, {"id": 220964, "content": "在b站搜他的相关", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 768915}, {"id": 220709, "content": "看球，一直喜欢的球星退役，微信朋友圈换成了他的背影照。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668349}, {"id": 220710, "content": "单曲循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1071561}, {"id": 221734, "content": "村上春树又落选后，默默买一本《和诺奖擦肩而过的男人》", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829541}]}